long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ChatGPT AutoClick Continue is a browser extension that automatically clicks on the 'Continue' button on the ChatGPT website. It simplifies the process of interacting with ChatGPT by eliminating the need for manual clicking on this button. It automatically clicks the 'Continue' button when you ask ChatGPT about code or text that exceeds the character limit.
